Technical Requirements

Framework: React (single .jsx file) or clean HTML — whatever produces the best result
Styling: Tailwind CSS or inline styles. Elegant, modern, mobile-responsive.
Color palette: Warm and inviting. Suggested: soft rose/blush tones, cream/ivory, gold accents, charcoal text. Avoid hot pink or anything that looks like official MK branding.
Typography: Clean, modern serif for headings (or elegant sans-serif), readable sans-serif for body
Images: Use placeholder image areas that Shelley can replace with her own photos. For now, use tasteful gradient backgrounds or abstract beauty-themed SVG patterns.
No external dependencies beyond what's available (React, Tailwind, Lucide icons)
Mobile-first responsive design
Performance: Fast, clean, minimal

